snippet.title: NanoMan Longplay
snippet.description: NanoMan; a tribute to an infuriating game you've probably heard of. This is full play-through that definitely contains spoilers for you lazy, impatient people. You can play it in your browser at http://www.lexaloffle.com/bbs/?pid=38516#p38515
